import React from 'react'
import { Col, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Category = () => {
  return (
    <Row>
        <Col  sm="12" className='justify-content-center d-flex cate'>
        <bu>الكل</bu>
        <bu>فطار</bu>
        <bu>غداء</bu>
        <bu>عشاء</bu>
        </Col>
        
    </Row>
  )
}

export default Category
